Get predicted data from fitted GAMs across period of observation, every
day

## Usage

``` r
anlz_prdday(mod)
```

## Arguments

- mod:

  input model object as returned by
  [`anlz_gam`](https://tbep-tech.github.io/wqtrends/reference/anlz_gam.md)

a `data.frame` with predictions
